(\bf{u}\cdot\bf{v})^2 \leq |\bf{u}|^2  |\bf{v}|^2
|\bf{u}\cdot\bf{v}| \leq |\bf{u}| |\bf{v}|
|\bf{u}|^2 + 2x(\bf{u}\cdot\bf{v}) +x^2|\bf{v}|^2\geq 0
